This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it focuses on the optimization algorithms for training deep neural network models. It may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks. Additionally, since deep learning models are widely used in computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), these sub-categories are also likely.
